{
  "stem": "979.4",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The tent blew open, you know, from the wind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then he came and picked us up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had told us, don't-- don't think that there's no gas chamber here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is one, he says.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- so he sent us to a warehouse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were all sleeping on the floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when he came in the-- in the morning, he says come on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says 100 of you-- out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we thought about the 100 that fit in the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I say, now they have no room, they're going to put us there?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the most-- the frightening thing I had since Auschwitz and then all that-- much more.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because when we-- we were marching, and there was, you know, like side roads.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we never passed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just keep on going-- and then another one, and another one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we came to the very last one, we saw there's no more walk.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's no more sidewalk to pass.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then I was holding [INAUDIBLE] this girl's friend, Julie, who was with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were holding-- we knew we were going to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were-- the feeling, you cannot explain it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were shaking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was saying my prayers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, please, don't let us suffer so much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I hope we die fast, we don't-- and all that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We really are scared to death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's the first-- the only place where I really was very scared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So-- but once we walked a little bit more, there was a tiny little area that we didn't see, a small little street.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We couldn't see it as we passed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He says, turn left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we went left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then they put us with-- at the barracks-- you know, the-- in a-- in a barrack.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
